2.0.0 (2018-04-19)

 - Support Redmine 4.x.
 - Dropped support for Redmine 3.x.

Claps for github.com/antitoine

1.0.0 (2016-12-22)

 - Dropped support for Redmine 2.x.
 - Only impersonate active users.
 - Use sudo mode if available.
 - Hide impersonation link in edit form.
 - Fix impersonation link when Redmine root is in subdirectory.
 - Support redmine_people plugin.

Most work since last release was done by github.com/thegcat.
Claps for him and plan.io team!


